This paper discusses the failure cases of deep learning models in ImageNet classification, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also aims to identify the challenges that current deep learning models are still vulnerable to, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper may involve some analysis of image patterns, which could be related to multimedia (cs.MM).
